Subject: [PATCH 07/17] Fix tearing crash with weak references

Replaces signal handlers with weak references to prevent crashes when
surfaces are destroyed. Uses g_object_weak_ref/unref instead of
destroy signal handlers to avoid accessing freed memory.

Signed-off-by: Vasiliy Stelmachenok <ventureo@cachyos.org>
